iles.wordpress.org/coffee2code">Scott Reilly</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/wonderboymusic">Scott Taylor</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/sergeybiryukov">Sergey Biryukov</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/shooper">Shawn Hooper</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/simonwheatley">Simon Wheatley</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/simonp303">simonp303</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/skaeser">skaeser</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/slobodanmanic">Slobodan Manic</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/socki03">socki03</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/solarissmoke">solarissmoke</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/stephdau">Stephane Daury</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/netweb">Stephen Edgar</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/stephenharris">Stephen Harris</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/stevegrunwell">Steve Grunwell</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/studionashvegas">studionashvegas</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/5um17">Sumit Singh</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tacoverdo">TacoVerdo</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/iamtakashi">Takashi Irie</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/miyauchi">Takayuki Miyauchi</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/karmatosed">Tammie</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tareq1988">Tareq Hasan</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tlovett1">Taylor Lovett</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ipm-frommen">Thorsten Frommen</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tillkruess">Till</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tmtrademark">tmtrademark</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tschutter">Tobias Schutter</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tobiasbg">TobiasBg</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tjnowell">Tom J Nowell</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tomasm">Tomas Mackevicius</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tomharrigan">TomHarrigan</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/topher1kenobe">Topher</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/zodiac1978">Torsten Landsiedel</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/liljimmi">Tracy Levesque</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/transom">transom</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/wpsmith">Travis Smith</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tywayne">tywayne</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/desaiuditd">Udit Desai</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/umeshsingla">Umesh Kumar</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/vinod-dalvi">Vinod Dalvi</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/vlajos">vlajos</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/voldemortensen">voldemortensen</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/westonruter">Weston Ruter</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/yoavf">Yoav Farhi</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/nobinobi">Yuta Sekine</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/zrothauser">Zack Rothauser</a>, and <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tollmanz">Zack Tollman</a>.</p>\n<p>Ils étaient 283 contributeurs pour cette version, il s&rsquo;agit d&rsquo;un nouveau record !.</p>\n<p>Si vous souhaitez les rejoindre la prochaine fois, faites un tour sur <a href="https://make.wordpress.org/">Make WordPress</a> et sur notre blog &laquo;&nbsp;<a href="https://make.wordpress.org/core/">core development&nbsp;&raquo;</a>.</p>\n<p>Merci d&rsquo;avoir choisi WordPress. Passez de merveilleuses fêtes de fin d&rsquo;année et à l&rsquo;année prochaine pour WordPress 4.2 !</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>La version française</h2>\n<p>Elle est d&rsquo;ores et déjà disponible au téléchargement <a href="http://fr.wordpress.org/">à cette adresse</a> !</p>\n<h4 class="wp-people-group">Les traducteurs qui ont oeuvrés sur cette version :</h4>\n<ul id="wp-people-group-validators" class="wp-people-group compact">\n<li id="wp-person-momo360modena" class="wp-person"><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/momo360modena"><img class="gravatar" src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/bd9516b368db97643f1cff5bf4c82123?s=30" alt="Amaury Balmer" /></a> <a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/momo360modena">Amaury Balmer</a></li>\n<li id="wp-person-xibe" class="wp-person"><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/xibe"><img class="gravatar" src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c16970a350d2de8ced3017a5a8514969?s=30" alt="Xavier Borderie" /></a> <a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/xibe">Xavier Borderie</a></li>\n<li class="wp-person"><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ben-kenobi"><img class="gravatar" src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/7bb495a607f1f7e4a231404a42b81936?s=30" alt="Benoit Catherineau" /></a> <a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ben-kenobi">Benoît Catherineau</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p class="wp-credits-list">&#8230; ainsi que<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ado666"> ado666</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dakotapearl">dakotapearl</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/fge0">Franck Gervais</a> et <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/jaddle">jaddle</a>.</p>\n<p class="wp-credits-list">C&rsquo;est grâce à eux que la version française est disponible en quasi simultanéité que la version originale. Merci à eux !</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 class="wp-credits-list">Ils en parlent aussi&#8230;</h2>\n<ul>\n<li class="wp-credits-list"><a href="https://wordpress.org/news/2014/12/dinah/">WordPress.org</a> (dont est tiré l&rsquo;article ci-dessus)</li>\n<li class="wp-credits-list"><a href="http://wptavern.com/wordpress-4-1-dinah-released">WP Tavern</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=wwuVe9q-5x0:h27tNRVwt-U:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=wwuVe9q-5x