; vos articles par exemple, ce dernier ne sera pas en mesure d&rsquo;importer les m&eacute;dias sur&hellip;</p>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" href="http://wpchannel.com/author/aurelien-denis/">Aur&eacute;lien Denis</a> - <a rel="nofollow" href="http://wpchannel.com/">WordPress Channel - Tutoriels, th&egrave;mes &amp; plugins WordPress</a> - <a rel="nofollow" href="http://wpchannel.com/exporter-medias-attaches-bibliotheque-wordpress/">Exporter les m&eacute;dias attach&eacute;s de votre biblioth&egrave;que WordPress</a></p>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:13;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"L''écho des plugins WordPress : Plugin Vulnerabilities";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:66:"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/plugin-vulnerabilities/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:66:"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/plugin-vulnerabilities/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2015-01-14T15:13:22+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"Li-An";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"<div>V&eacute;rifiez si vos plugins n''ont pas de faille connue</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:14;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"WordPress Francophone : L’Hebdo WordPress n°250 : Je suis Charlie";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/LSx7EEVudz8/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/LSx7EEVudz8/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2015-01-13T22:20:08+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Benoît";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2612:"<div>\n<p>La semaine pass&eacute;e a &eacute;t&eacute; marqu&eacute;e par une actualit&eacute; bien triste, celle du massacre de journalistes et de dessinateurs du c&eacute;l&egrave;bre Charlie Hebdo, de policiers, mais aussi de gens qui ont eu le malheur de se trouver au mauvais endroit au mauvais moment&hellip; N&rsquo;oublions pas ! &hellip; N&rsquo;oublions surtout pas cette chance que nous avons de pouvoir exprimer nos id&eacute;es quelles qu&rsquo;elles soient.</p>\n<p>Notre communaut&eacute; existe gr&acirc;ce &agrave; cette libert&eacute;, WordPress aussi par extension. #JeSuisCharlie #NousSommesCharlie</p>\n<p><em><a href="http://boiteaweb.fr/je-suis-charlie-8500.html">Montrez votre soutien gr&acirc;ce &agrave; l&rsquo;extension de Julio</a></em>.</p>\n<h2>L&rsquo;Hebdo</h2>\n<h3>Le WordCamp Paris 2015 c&rsquo;est dans 10 jours</h3>\n<p>Eh oui ! D&eacute;j&agrave; ! &hellip; <a href="http://www.nicolas-birckel.fr/2015/01/09/a-la-fin-du-mois-je-serais-a-wordcamp-paris-2015-et-vous/">Nicolas Birckel en parle</a>. Et vous ?</p>\n<h3>BuddyPress 2.2 beta 1</h3>\n<p>BuddyPress 2.2 poursuit son d&eacute;veloppement et <a href="https://buddypress.org/2015/01/buddypress-2-2-beta-1/">sort en beta 1</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>Passons &agrave; table n&deg;10 : FX B&eacute;nard</h3>\n<p><a href="http://wpmarmite.com/pat-episode-010/">Interview de FX B&eacute;nard</a> par WPMarmite.</p>\n<h3>Int&eacute;grer Slack dans WordPress</h3>\n<p>Voici comment <a href="http://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-integrate-slack-with-wordpress/">int&eacute;grer Slack dans WordPress</a> (en).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=LSx7EEVudz8:uiNzUjFREj8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=LSx7EEVudz8:uiNzUjFREj8:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=LSx7EEVudz8:uiNzUjFREj8:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a href="htt